{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":587300,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那我不做人了","timestamp":1605853225,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587301,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不，这就是动物本能。又当又立就算了","timestamp":1605853235,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587307,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"的确，理中客这种共识并不比其他的高贵","timestamp":1605853270,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587319,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"确实","timestamp":1605853417,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587350,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"没有理中客，人类早就被失控的疯子们拉着冲下悬崖了","timestamp":1605853670,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587398,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"《乌合之众》","timestamp":1605853968,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587426,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: “理性”都是到了古希腊才广为人所知，那之前的人们也创造了辉煌的文明，比如古埃及的金字塔和数学。还有与世隔绝的玛雅文明专精天文，他们甚至从不知道“理性”。","timestamp":1605854212,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587510,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":122171,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"画重点，“为人所知”","timestamp":1605854811,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":122171,"reply":8,"tag":null,"text":"理中客们拒绝承认的是，共识比事实更重要，共识而非真理是社会的基础。\n实验科学出现之前一样有伟大的文明，对本不存在的神明的信仰一样使人创造出辉煌灿烂的艺术。人类可以为了一个共识去屠杀，也可以为了一个共识而牺牲，共识背后有没有科学和逻辑的支撑都无关紧要。\n正如人不需要在乎人种在生物学上究竟有多大区别，人也不需要在乎一个人能否代表人群，这种不分场合、罔顾事实，仅凭一个“我们认为”就可以开始行动的意志，才是人既区别于工具理性、也区别于动物本能的地方。","timestamp":1605853072,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782654,"url":"","vote":{}}}